videos.description: Notre Dame's Prentiss Hubb pokes the ball away from Ohio State and Nate Laszewski is able to capitalize with a huge flush and foul in the final seconds of the half.

videos.headline: Notre Dame's Laszewski fired up after and-1 slam

videos.description: Ohio State's E.J. Liddell tries to shake Notre Dame's defense before rising for a slam, but Prentiss Hubb is there for a rejection and staredown.

videos.description: E.J. Liddell pulls up for a deep jumper just in time as the shot clock expires with under a minute left to play vs. Notre Dame.
